{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"嘶声","listener":null,"text":"你老人家无论对孩儿怎样，都是应当的，你老人家何必说这样的话……但……但孩儿今日能听着你老人家这番话，便是立刻就死了，也是……也是高兴的了……","tone":"嘶声","chapter":50,"line_start":2,"line_end":2},{"speaker":"char_yun_yi","speaker_name":"云翼缓缓","listener":null,"text":"铁血大旗门，如今已只剩下我们四个人，从现在起，到我死之日，我必要善待你们，只因……","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_yun_jiu_xiao","speaker_name":"云九霄","listener":null,"text":"大哥，你还是歇歇吧！","tone":"无奈","chapter":50,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_yun_yi","speaker_name":"云翼惨笑","listener":null,"text":"这些话我必定要说下去的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":50,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_yun_jiu_xiao","speaker_name":"云九霄垂首","listener":null,"text":"但……但大哥不说，我们也知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"他语声突变激昂，接道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_wen_dai_dai","speaker_name":"温黛黛突然大声","listener":null,"text":"我等五人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_yun_yi","speaker_name":"云翼","listener":null,"text":"你怎能算是大旗门人？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":50,"line_start":32,"line_end":32},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"缓缓","listener":null,"text":"你当真要如此？","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_wen_dai_dai","speaker_name":"温黛黛","listener":null,"text":"若怕吃苦，我早就去死了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"厉叱","listener":null,"text":"你当真有为大旗门效死之决心？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":50,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_wen_dai_dai","speaker_name":"温黛黛","listener":null,"text":"温黛黛生为大旗门人，死为大旗门鬼。","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_yun_yi","speaker_name":"云翼","listener":null,"text":"你可知本门铁血两字之意？","tone":"陈述","chapter":50,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_wen_dai_dai","speaker_name":"温黛黛垂首",